================================================================================
EXTERNAL DATA & CONTENT SOURCES
================================================================================

NexusM can optionally retrieve metadata and artwork from third-party online
services. This content is owned by its respective providers and is subject to
their terms; NexusM does not redistribute it and only fetches it on the user's
behalf when an API key is configured.

  Service          Content                       Attribution / Terms
  ───────────────  ────────────────────────────  ──────────────────────────────────────
  fanart.tv        Movie / TV posters, backdrops  Images licensed CC BY 3.0 — attribution
                                                  required. © fanart.tv contributors.
                                                  https://fanart.tv
  TMDB             Movie / TV metadata, images    This product uses the TMDB API but is
                                                  not endorsed or certified by TMDB.
                                                  https://www.themoviedb.org
  TVmaze           TV metadata                    Data under CC BY-SA 4.0 (licensing terms
                                                  per TVmaze API). https://www.tvmaze.com

